name: MySQL5

getPSDEDataQueryCodeConds.customCond:
EXISTS(SELECT * FROM `IBZDCSYSTEM` t21 
LEFT OUTER JOIN `IBZROLE` t31 ON t21.`DCSYSTEMID` = t31.`DCSYSTEMID` 
 WHERE 
 t11.`PSSYSTEMID` = t21.`SYSTEMID`  AND  EXISTS(SELECT * FROM `IBZUSER_ROLE` t41 
 WHERE 
 t31.`SYS_ROLEID` = t41.`SYS_ROLEID`  AND  ( t41.`USERID` = #{ctx.sessioncontext.srfpersonid} ) )  AND  ( ( t31.`AUTHORIZEALL` = 0  OR  t31.`AUTHORIZEALL` IS NULL ) )  AND  ( t21.`SRFDCID` = #{ctx.sessioncontext.srfdcid}  AND  ( t21.`SYSPERMISSION` IS NULL  OR  t21.`SYSPERMISSION` = 'ALL' ) ) )
getPSDEDataQueryCodeConds.name: 查询条件

queryCode:
SELECT
t1.`APPCATEGORY`,
t1.`CREATEDATE`,
t1.`CREATEMAN`,
t1.`ICON`,
t1.`ICONCSS`,
t1.`MOBILEAPP`,
t1.`PERMISSIONTAG`,
t1.`PSSYSAPPFUNCID`,
t1.`PSSYSAPPFUNCNAME`,
t1.`PSSYSTEMAPPID`,
t1.`PSSYSTEMAPPNAME`,
t1.`SHOWORDER`,
t1.`SRFDCID`,
t1.`SYSTEMID`,
t1.`TIP`,
t1.`UPDATEDATE`,
t1.`UPDATEMAN`,
t1.`URL`,
t1.`VIEWPATHPARAMS`
FROM `IBZPSSYSAPPFUNC` t1 
LEFT JOIN `IBZPSSYSTEM` t11 ON t1.`SYSTEMID` = t11.`PSSYSTEMID`
